Rating: 4
This is easy and super tasty! I don't know what other reviewers are talking about when they say the chicken is bland...maybe they didn't season it enough? Or maybe they tried to "cut the fat" and didn't cook it in butter and oil? I've made this multiple times, and each time it's been excellent. Be sure to use fresh corn (frozen or canned will leave you with chewy corn). I usually double the relish because it's so delicious.

