Rating: 3
Very tasty, but it needed some enhancements. I used red onion instead of green onion and I added some minced garlic to the tomato mixture. For the chicken, I deglazed the pan with some white wine and minced garlic, then added some fresh lemon juice and 1/2 tblspn butter to the pan before returning the chicken to the pan for a quick rewarm before serving. I served this with rice pilaf and steamed asparagus - very yummy!

