This recipe needs to have some seasoning - a major dose of seasoning, as a matter of fact! There is a Bon Appetite recipe from the late '70's, with almost the same ingredients, but with a cumin viniagrette - 100% better. Ignore this one and find something else to make use of wonderful ingredients.